{{Infobox person | name = Kari Aagaard | birth_name = | birth_date = <!-- {{Birth date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} or {{Birth-date and age|Month DD, YYYY}} --> | birth_place = | death_date = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} or {{Death-date and age|Month DD, YYYY|Month DD, YYYY}} (death date then birth date) --> | death_place = | nationality = Norwegian | other_names = | known_for = | occupation = }} '''Kari Aagaard''' is a Norwegian [[team handball|handball]] player. She played 92 matches for the [[Norway women's national handball team]] between 1973 and 1978.<ref name=nhf>{{cite web|url=http://www.handball.no/Statistikk_Landskamper.asp?LagId=6014&SpillerId=8379 |title=Landskampstatistikk. Totaloversikt for Aagaard, Kari |publisher=[[Norwegian Handball Federation]] |date= |language=Norwegian |accessdate=29 December 2010}}</ref> She participated at the [[1973 World Women's Handball Championship|1973]] and [[1975 World Women's Handball Championship]].
